metadata.name: Letting Go
metadata.description:
There's a time to hold on, and a time to let go; and the wise one knows the difference. So, let go of the things that brings you down, do not serve your growth, your future & the person you're becoming.

Created with Adobe Photoshop & After Effects
Time: ~25 hrs
Size: 2700 x 3600 pixels; 300ppi
